      <heading>Mon Nov 22 (Larannea)   :: 2: Seekers/Sponsors.</heading>
      <slot>2</slot>
      <level>203</level>
      <author>0</author>
      <date>0</date>
      <text>. The seekers for the Kin guild will be split into two groups:
. 
. 1: Seekers that were guilded to either the TAS or the RAS guild...RP wise
.    these are mostly runaways and such. Since they allready have proven to
.    be able to roleplay (by getting into these guilds) they will only need
.    one sponsor. This being the person who finds them.
.
. 2: Seekers that have not been guilded to either the TAS or RAS guild.
.    These seekers need to gain 3 sponsors within 3 weeks time. If they did
.    not get enough sponsors within these three weeks I will talk with
.    them. If they say they did not have 3 sponsor roleplays they will be
.    granted more time and I will urge the members to roleplay with seekers
.    more. If they did have enough roleplay but just didnt get the sponsors
.    then I will tell them that they are not ready to be guilded or
.    something along those lines.
.
. Apart from this:
. All seekers must submit a background history to me before they start
. seeking.
</text>
