      <text>I figured I'd make a small, quick statement about the guarded rank and
also about the patient rank. These two ranks are mostly intended for
people that are new to the guild or that might be guilded here for a short
period of time. As such, they will not always be aware of the Kin. It might
not even always be the best idea to inform them about the ic existance
of the Kin. As such, keep this in mind when RP-ing with guarded and patient
ranks and use your personal judgement on what you will be telling and wonr
be telling this person ICly.

Laran.
</text>
