some of these Novices and Accepted ran away from the Tower while others
might have been kicked out.

If any of you happen to be approached by a runaway Novice (or Accepted)
then you should inform OOCly if they wish to be returned to the Tower or
if they would like to join the Kin. This is a choice that they only can
make. Either way, it will be good for Kin RP...

If they wish to be returned to the Tower, however, then it might be best
for you to NPC another wisewoman to prevent yourself from being ICly
exposed.

In addition, for the moment it is more realistic for the Kin to deliver
any and all runaways to the Tower rather then to Salidar, seeying there
havent been any real indepth IC contacts between Salidar and the Kin.

If you have any questions about this, please contact me...I myself am
a bit boggled that I wrote this but at the same time, it seems to be
good to have written this down.

Laran.
