Since I am the person who made the decision on that skill, allow me to
share my thinking on it. The Kin are failed novices and accepted. Some
failed because they lacked the necessary strength in the One Power, some
because they refused to go through the testing ter'angreal, and some for
severely breaking rules. In the Sedai guilds, the teach skill is only
given to Sedai, not to Accepted or Novices. Thus, for gskills the Kin has
what Accepted and Novices would have, as well as the herb knowledge they
gain to carry out their guise as wise women. What this means is that
although you do not have teach, you do have stormshield.

Cappen
