Amarinda and I have been discussing this guild a bit lately and how it
fits in with the MUD. This prompted us to look at the guildinfo and be
quite honestly dumbfounded. Considering the membership numbers of the Kin
in the books, it is ... well, ludicrous to assume that every last blasted
one of them had a strong affinity for Healing. In fact, I'd surmise that
the reason the Wise Women use herbs is as much because a lot of them need
them as it is to help with their disguise. I realize that some allowances
have to be made because this is a MUD and not the books, but when the
entire guild is supposed to be composed of failed novices and accepted and
perhaps 3 or 4 of the members are the only ones who fit that bill, something
is a bit wrong. Some of the ranks are really curious. Instructor, for
example. I'm also really confused about why warders and aes sedai are
guilded here, too.

Expect changes.
